ime":"2017-03-13T17:36:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪得排骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係  極度困擾"},{"pid":"661cd3f8a102286c632c7532801b03057b107c48","tid":155042,"uid":83531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:37:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你係咪得排骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係  極度困擾</blockquote><br />\n我分啲脂肪比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6708fa141a642cf3af7877df2fbff03c747618b","tid":155042,"uid":87417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>循例問下<br />\n<br />\n增肥定增肌</blockquote><br />\n其實呢D食極唔肥 case已經唔理增肥定增肌, 有方法令個身厚D多D肉已經好感恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 增左廿年都係過輕, 依家食慾仲要冇發育期咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我依家只係增肌安慰下自己 同著衫可以carry到個shape出黎<br />\n不過4肢都係成碌柴咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5b1e185bd4404d520770ac8d66ce29a57a6d54","tid":155042,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:43:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>循例問下<br />\n<br />\n增肥定增肌</blockquote><br />\n貪心D  兩樣都增得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n增肥+肌 飲gainer<br />\n增肌 飲whey<br />\n<br />\n另外要均衡飲食 食多d菜幫助消化吸收<br />\n外國gym撚好鐘意西蘭花 唔知有冇關係"},{"pid":"3fe3e47e9a1220ff381e79e5a6a05c6277b26280","tid":155042,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"試下飲開胃茶<br />\n我細個都係好瘦<br />\n屋企人煲過一次開胃茶之後 <br />\n胃口好咗好多<br />\n<br />\nBMI 22"},{"pid":"26f9c66e50cf20b625a9ad36f4dfe1263eecd6b2","tid":155042,"uid":52494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:46:30.000Z","msg":"計下自己tedd 先"},{"pid":"a6c7d20bc34c2455dae17ee76a7633c775da3609","tid":155042,"uid":91240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T18:11:10.000Z","msg":"去考一次DSE 日日係屋企温書 <br />\n你就知點增肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c347119391b9e2ed70884440a27abbc2fb4417","tid":155042,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T18:17:01.000Z","msg":"長年51 52 試過增肥好多次 都唔成功<br />\n<br />\n後尾睇到篇文 之後自己半年左右上到60<br />\n首先要大量食野 頭3個月直頭係唔理油鹽糖肥唔肥 乜都食 當然要同時做gym 一日4 5餐<br />\n後尾3個月 就食到好清 一日都係4 5餐 再一日兩杯gainer 一星期操5日/6日<br />\n重點既係 要做運動 單嘗大量飲食唔做運動根據我過往既經驗唔多肥到"},{"pid":"5e2b4bf3079a7048717433c4c92e9893815df230","tid":155042,"uid":34683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T18:22:21.000Z","msg":"你自己計一日吸收幾多卡路里先啦<br />\n唔係話食幾多碗飯同幾多肉就會肥<br />\n<br />\n你想知我再教你"},{"pid":"13b6979d17039e84875995017bccd550fd9ec5bf","tid":155042,"uid":87417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T19:01:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去考一次DSE 日日係屋企温書 <br />\n你就知點增肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n準備考dse個人仲瘦呀  <br />\n依家先好返DD"},{"pid":"e73221add5a77023f9c0d8233627ba4425230739","tid":155042,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:41:23.000Z","msg":"181cm 54kg<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nChing 而家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a2db7052ee8a58d9500db026742c4e4668ba9b","tid":155042,"uid":87417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e73221add5a77023f9c0d8233627ba4425230739","tid":155042,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,